WEBVTT

00:04:58.226 --> 00:05:00.110
So relax, do it again.

00:05:00.110 --> 00:05:02.878
All right, so right now,

00:05:02.878 --> 00:05:07.279
your brain is controlling your arm
and it's also controlling his arm,

00:05:07.279 --> 00:05:09.471
so go ahead and just do it one more time.

00:05:09.471 --> 00:05:11.504
All right, so it's perfect. (Laughter)

00:05:11.504 --> 00:05:15.265
So now, what would happen
if I took over my control of your hand?

00:05:15.265 --> 00:05:17.508
And so, just relax your hand.

00:05:17.508 --> 00:05:19.726
What happens?

00:05:19.726 --> 00:05:20.760
Ah, nothing.

00:05:20.760 --> 00:05:22.298
Why not?

00:05:22.298 --> 00:05:23.993
Because the brain has to do it.

00:05:23.993 --> 00:05:25.307
So you do it again.

00:05:25.346 --> 00:05:27.780
All right, that's perfect.

00:05:27.780 --> 00:05:30.319
Thank you guys for being
such a good sport.